This is to build sdcard image for tinkerboard 3:

Info on tinkerboard 3: https://github.com/TinkerBoard/TinkerBoard/wiki/Tinker-Board-3-&-3S#116-asus-api-documentation

Parts needed:
1. tinkerboard 3.
2. Sandisk 64GB micro sdcard.    ( install u-boot in on board spi )
3. Host PC with ubuntu 24.
4. USB2 SATA SSD
5. usb3 stick.

Steps to build tinkerboard 3 sdcard image:

1. git clone https://github.com/philipchen888/build-tinkerboard.git
   sudo apt update
   sudo apt upgrade
   sudo apt-get install build-essential git libssl-dev nmap net-tools libncurses-dev dnsutils vsftpd ftp binfmt-support qemu-user-static scons libdbus-glib-1-dev libbluetooth-dev python3-dev python3-pip python3-setuptools libcurl4-openssl-dev gettext dbus-x11 chrpath diffstat gawk texinfo curl flex bison device-tree-compiler swig libmpc-dev debootstrap debhelper kpartx gdisk devscripts isolinux po4a libgnutls28-dev mtools python-is-python3 python3-pyelftools u-boot-tools gcc-aarch64-linux-gnu

   wget https://releases.linaro.org/components/toolchain/binaries/latest-7/aarch64-linux-gnu/gcc-linaro-7.5.0-2019.12-x86_64_aarch64-linux-gnu.tar.xz
   sudo tar xvf gcc-linaro-7.5.0-2019.12-x86_64_aarch64-linux-gnu.tar.xz  -C /usr/local/

2. Install live-build:
   sudo apt-get install debootstrap debhelper kpartx gdisk devscripts isolinux po4a live-build

   lb --version ( 3.0~a57-1 /usr/bin/lb )

   For trixie, bookworm and forky:
   wget http://deb.debian.org/debian/pool/main/l/live-build/live-build_20250814.tar.xz
   tar xvf live-build_20250814.tar.xz
   cd live-build
   sudo make install
   lb --version ( 20250814 /usr/bin/lb )

3. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/uboot  ( Download u-boot to spi )
   git clone https://github.com/TinkerBoard-Linux/rockchip-linux-rkbin --depth=1 -b linux5.10-rk356x
   mv rockchip-linux-rkbin rkbin
   git clone https://github.com/TinkerBoard-Linux/rockchip-linux-u-boot --depth=1 -b linux5.10-rk356x
   mv rockchip-linux-u-boot u-boot
   change tinker_board_3_defconfig to enable UEFI boot.
   make u-boot

   The results are in ./out/u-boot.img, idbloader.img, trust.img, uboot-trust-spi.img

   Plugin sdcard to PC.
   sudo ./mkuboot.sh
   Eject sdcard from PC.

   Plugin sdcard to tinkerboard 3.
   Also you can burn uboot-trust-spi.img to tinkerboard 3 spi flash.

4. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/linux ( Compile vendor kernel 5.10 )
   git clone https://github.com/TinkerBoard-Linux/rockchip-linux-kernel.git --depth=1 -b linux5.10-rk356x
   mv rockchip-linux-kernel linux
   vi ./linux/arch/arm64/configs/tinker_board_3_defconfig ( delete RTL8822CE, AP6XXX )
   make kernel

   The results are in ./linux/tmp/lib/modules/*
                      ./linux/tmp/boot/*

5. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/rootfs-bookworm  ( Compile debian bookworm rootfs )
   make rootfs
   The results are in ./linaro-rootfs.img linaro-esp.img
   make clean

6. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/rootfs-trixie  ( Compile debian trixie rootfs )
   make rootfs
   The results are in ./linaro-rootfs.img linaro-esp.img
   make clean

7. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/rootfs-forky  ( Compile debian forky rootfs )
   make rootfs
   The results are in ./linaro-rootfs.img linaro-esp.img
   make clean

8. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/rootfs-ubuntu-noble  ( Compile ubuntu-noble rootfs )
   make rootfs
   The results are in ./linaro-rootfs.img linaro-esp.img
   make clean

9. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/rootfs-ubuntu-questing  ( Compile ubuntu-questing rootfs )
   make rootfs
   The results are in ./linaro-rootfs.img linaro-esp.img
   make clean

10. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/bookworm-gnome  ( Build debian bookworm gnome-desktop image )
    Plugin usb3 stick to PC.
    sudo ./mksdcardimg.sh
    Eject usb3 stick from PC.

11. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/trixie-gnome    ( Build debian trixie gnome-desktop image )
    Plugin usb3 stick to PC.
    sudo ./mksdcardimg.sh
    Eject usb3 stick from PC.

12. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/forky-gnome     ( Build debian forky gnome-desktop image )
    Plugin usb3 stick to PC.
    sudo ./mksdcardimg.sh
    Eject usb3 stick from PC.

13. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/ubuntu-noble  ( Build ubuntu-noble image )
    Plugin usb3 stick to PC.
    sudo ./mksdcardimg.sh
    Eject usb3 stick from PC.

14. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/ubuntu-questing  ( Build ubuntu-questing image )
    Plugin usb3 stick to PC.
    sudo ./mksdcardimg.sh
    Eject usb3 stick from PC.

15. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/android       ( Build android image )

16. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/bookworm-flightaware  ( flightaware in bookworm )

17. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/yocto         ( Build yocto desktop image )

18. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/buildroot     ( Build buildroot image )

19. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/bookworm-gpio ( Build bookworm gpio tests )

20. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/fedora        ( Build fedora image )

21. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/ubuntu-uefi   ( Build ubuntu-uefi image )

22. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/bookworm-uefi ( Build bookworm-uefi image )

23. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/trixie-uefi   ( Build trixie-uefi image )

24. cd ~/build-tinkerboard/forky-uefi    ( Build forky-uefi image )
